short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Preview sites' Discord embeds for debugging purposes. Not affiliated in any way with Discord.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An open-source tool to help web developers test their sites' embeds as they would look in Discord. The aim of this tool is to eliminate the tedious process of evading Discord's embed cache, and eliminate the need to deploy the site somewhere to test it (which might expose unannounced projects prematurely). This tool provides a simple preview window of the Discord embed.
